Package example.myCommands

Class Command

java.lang.Object
example.myCommands.Command
Direct Known Subclasses:
AddCommand, AddIfMaxCommand, AddIfMinCommand, ClearCommand, ExecuteScriptCommand, ExitCommand, HelpCommand, InfoCommand, PrintFieldDescendingCategoryCommand, PrintFieldDescendingMeleeWeaponCommand, PrintUniqueHealthCommand, RemoveByIdCommand, RemoveLowerCommand, SaveCommand, ShowCommand, UpdateByIdCommand
public abstract class Command extends Object
The Command class is an abstract class that defines a command that can be executed on a MyLinkedList object. Contains a reference to the MyLinkedList object on which the command will be executed.
